title: Geno's Italian Deli
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Typical Italian food with pasta and pizza where menu is dominated by meat and dairy but a few of the vegetarian items can be requested vegan, such as the eggplant veggie burger wrap. Tell your server if you want something without egg or cheese - they will work with you.
